* Other apprentices can join or oppose you
* Partner choice affects difficulty significantly
* Some characters refuse to partner with others

== Rune Secrets ==

=== Rune Locations ===
The 7 Runes are scattered across the world:
* Earth Rune - Lemele region
* Water Rune - Aquatic area
* Fire Rune - Volcanic region
* Wind Rune - Sky-related location
* Light Rune - Temple area
* Star Rune - Hidden location
* Moon Rune - Final dungeon area

=== Rune Effects ===
Each Rune provides passive bonuses:
* Stats increase
* Resistance to elements
* Story progression unlocked

