== Difficulty Secrets ==

=== Scaling System ===
Enemy stats scale with your level:
* Grinding too much makes the game harder
* Optimal levels exist for each area
* Apprentice battles are particularly affected

=== Apprentice Battles ===
Other apprentices level up with you:
* Their stats scale aggressively
* Fighting them early is easier
* Losing gives the opponent your Runes

== Tips ==

'''Leveling Strategy:'''
* Don't over-grind
* Progress when able to clear areas
* Use inns frequently

'''Money Management:'''
* Equipment is expensive
* Sell unused items
* Prioritize defense upgrades

'''Boss Fights:'''
* Save before all boss encounters
* Learn attack patterns
* Use buff/debuff spells

== Crystal Ball ==

The Crystal Ball shows nearby features:
* Green dots = towns/points of interest
* Red dots = enemies
* Rune locations revealed as you approach

== Multiple Endings ==

Your character choice and actions affect the ending:
* Each character has unique dialogue
* Partner choice affects outcome
* Certain NPCs have different responses

== Easter Eggs ==

