== Known Issues ==

=== Battery Save ===
* Game uses battery save
* Single save file
* Corrupted saves mean total loss

=== Difficulty Curve ===
* Game is considered one of the harder SNES RPGs
* Apprentice scaling can create difficulty spikes
* Patience required for completion

